{
  "stem": "365.2",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was in-- I was 15 years old.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I said, I am not going to give them the satisfaction of crying out, you know, when they lash me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I bit my lips till they were bleeding, but I didn't let out a peep out of me.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "When he finished with the 40 lashes, I remember I could only-- I could not straighten out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I walked away like animal on all fours.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I crawled away from the stool.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So the commandant went over and grabbed the lash from the couple that was meting out the lashing, and he hit me right across the head.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "The lash split my head right up-- I still bear a scar here.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Blood was coming down my head, because the heads were cleaned, clipped to the skin, no hair then that.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he says to me, you little [GERMAN], which means a pig, dog.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "You [GERMAN], you little pig, dog-- when he hit me across the head, and he walked away.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then the couple comes over to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I'll use his exact words, what he said to me. 'You little son of a bitch, he says.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "What are you playing?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Trying to play hero?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You have more luck than brains that he didn't kill you on the spot, because on many occasions, I have seen where a prisoner wouldn't scream from pain, that he would go [INAUDIBLE] with his stiletto.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He would kill him on the spot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was blue in the face, because from all the prisoners were screaming, and you were the youngest, and you didn't let out a peep.",
      "word_count": 26
    }
  ],
